00:44:48.800 --> 00:44:51.030
is because you've limited Me and how I'm

00:44:51.040 --> 00:44:56.910
able to refine

00:44:56.910 --> 00:44:56.920
you.'I've

00:44:56.920 --> 00:44:58.350
had enough; I don't want any more

00:44:58.360 --> 00:45:01.190
refining.

00:45:01.200 --> 00:45:03.030
He said, 'But Brandon, My heart is for

00:45:03.040 --> 00:45:06.430
you to go from glory to

00:45:06.430 --> 00:45:06.440
glory.'He's

00:45:06.440 --> 00:45:08.590
changing me

00:45:08.590 --> 00:45:08.600
into

00:45:08.600 --> 00:45:13.430
His likeness

00:45:13.440 --> 00:45:17.390
and image to perfect in me the love of

00:45:17.400 --> 00:45:20.750
God shown to the world. For

00:45:22.680 --> 00:45:27.030
He's changing me from earthly things to

00:45:27.040 --> 00:45:29.070
the heavenlies. He's changing

00:45:29.070 --> 00:45:29.080
you into

00:45:29.080 --> 00:45:33.150
His likeness and image to perfect in

00:45:33.150 --> 00:45:33.160
you

00:45:33.160 --> 00:45:37.470
the love of God shown to the world

00:45:37.480 --> 00:45:43.670
from glory to glory.

00:46:30.520 --> 00:46:32.670
Many people, when they get to a

00:46:32.680 --> 00:46:34.590
certain level,

00:46:34.600 --> 00:46:36.790
like I saw with

00:46:36.800 --> 00:46:39.230
an old pastor—he wanted 10,000 members

00:46:39.240 --> 00:46:40.750
so bad,

00:46:40.760 --> 00:46:43.190
he had a goal of 10,000 members,

00:46:43.200 --> 00:46:45.670
and for the 13-plus years that

00:46:45.680 --> 00:46:48.790
we worked there, we never achieved it;

00:46:48.800 --> 00:46:51.190
we made it to

00:46:51.190 --> 00:46:51.200
8,500.

00:46:51.200 --> 00:46:53.110
We made it to 85. Some Easter Sundays we

00:46:53.120 --> 00:46:55.110
would bust 15.

00:46:55.120 --> 00:46:57.750
But his whole goal was to get to

00:46:57.760 --> 00:47:00.790
a certain amount. It was his focus.

00:47:00.800 --> 00:47:01.870
And the Lord started showing me. He

00:47:01.880 --> 00:47:05.830
said, "If your focus is

00:47:05.840 --> 00:47:10.030
that, you're missing it.

00:47:10.040 --> 00:47:12.830
Outward growth for man's

00:47:12.830 --> 00:47:12.840
approval—you're

00:47:12.840 --> 00:47:15.190
missing it. Growth should always

00:47:15.200 --> 00:47:18.470
be to impact my kingdom,

00:47:18.480 --> 00:47:21.110
from glory to glory, for the

00:47:21.120 --> 00:47:22.950
souls,

00:47:22.960 --> 00:47:25.190
for healings,

00:47:25.190 --> 00:47:25.200
and

00:47:25.200 --> 00:47:27.710
demonstration. But if it's ever just for

00:47:27.720 --> 00:47:31.310
ego—if

00:47:31.320 --> 00:47:33.390
it ever comes about just being for

00:47:33.390 --> 00:47:33.400
ego—I'll

00:47:33.400 --> 00:47:37.830
never allow it.

00:47:37.840 --> 00:47:41.070
Ego is a destroyer."So many times

00:47:41.070 --> 00:47:41.080
I've—like

00:47:41.080 --> 00:47:43.230
even with this last blessed

00:47:43.230 --> 00:47:43.240
brother—he

00:47:43.240 --> 00:47:45.950
showed me

00:47:45.960 --> 00:47:47.990
his church this weekend.

00:47:48.000 --> 00:47:49.830
He said, "I want you to come here and

00:47:49.840 --> 00:47:51.310
I'll help you get a home. I'll do

00:47:51.320 --> 00:47:53.590
all these

00:47:53.600 --> 00:47:54.910
things."One

00:47:54.920 --> 00:47:58.590
of the largest churches in America

00:47:58.600 --> 00:47:59.910
offered me

00:47:59.920 --> 00:48:02.270
finances to bless my family, big money

00:48:02.280 --> 00:48:04.030
to help us.

00:48:04.040 --> 00:48:07.870
And

00:48:07.880 --> 00:48:10.830
I was like, "This is God,

00:48:10.840 --> 00:48:12.830
Lord. This is you. It has

00:48:12.840 --> 00:48:14.310
to be

00:48:14.310 --> 00:48:14.320
you."But

00:48:14.320 --> 00:48:15.830
the Lord said to me,

00:48:15.840 --> 00:48:17.510
"Are you going to deliberately disobey

00:48:17.520 --> 00:48:20.310
what I've asked you to

00:48:20.310 --> 00:48:20.320
do?"I

00:48:20.320 --> 00:48:22.830
said, "What do you mean?

00:48:22.840 --> 00:48:25.070
Any blessings from you, right? Any open

00:48:25.080 --> 00:48:27.030
door has to be from you."He

00:48:27.030 --> 00:48:27.040
said,

00:48:27.040 --> 00:48:29.910
"No, I told you to sit on the back row

00:48:29.910 --> 00:48:29.920
and

00:48:29.920 --> 00:48:35.150
pray at this little

00:48:35.150 --> 00:48:35.160
church."You

00:48:35.160 --> 00:48:36.550
know, I realize that maybe my

00:48:36.560 --> 00:48:40.190
character can't handle that yet.

00:48:40.200 --> 00:48:42.750
Maybe my character can't handle a church

00:48:42.760 --> 00:48:45.870
with 40,000 or 50,000 people.

00:48:45.880 --> 00:48:48.390
Maybe I can do this behind a camera

00:48:48.390 --> 00:48:48.400
because

00:48:48.400 --> 00:48:50.750
I don't see you

00:48:50.750 --> 00:48:50.760
face

00:48:50.760 --> 00:48:52.990
to

00:48:52.990 --> 00:48:53.000
face.

00:48:53.000 --> 00:48:54.150
I don't know.

00:48:54.160 --> 00:48:57.270
What is God protecting me from?

00:48:57.280 --> 00:48:59.790
From myself.

00:48:59.800 --> 00:49:02.990
I could go anywhere in any

00:49:03.000 --> 00:49:05.150
church because I've been offered it so many

00:49:05.160 --> 00:49:06.830
times, but every single time it's

00:49:06.840 --> 00:49:08.870
always to a little

00:49:08.880 --> 00:49:10.510
congregation with just several hundred

00:49:10.520 --> 00:49:11.550
people.

00:49:11.560 --> 00:49:17.910
Sit on the back row. Humble yourself.

00:49:17.920 --> 00:49:19.910
And I think it's very interesting because

00:49:19.910 --> 00:49:19.920
the

00:49:19.920 --> 00:49:21.310
same said, "Don't forget

00:49:21.320 --> 00:49:24.790
the janitor.

00:49:24.800 --> 00:49:27.310
I'll make you a household

00:49:27.320 --> 00:49:29.590
name throughout this for me, not for

00:49:29.600 --> 00:49:30.510
you.

00:49:30.520 --> 00:49:32.390
I'll not share my glory with you at all,

00:49:32.400 --> 00:49:34.390
but you can speak for me.

00:49:34.400 --> 00:49:36.070
And I allow you to give these words

00:49:36.080 --> 00:49:38.310
and they'll prove to be accurate.

00:49:38.320 --> 00:49:40.310
But anytime you ever get a big head

00:49:40.320 --> 00:49:41.910
about it,

00:49:41.910 --> 00:49:41.920
it's

00:49:41.920 --> 00:49:44.550
taken that fast.

00:49:44.560 --> 00:49:47.790
You're just a glove and

00:49:47.800 --> 00:49:49.350
the Holy Spirit fills the glove and he

00:49:49.360 --> 00:49:51.630
makes the glove operate.

00:49:51.640 --> 00:49:54.950
You can do nothing apart from me.

00:49:54.960 --> 00:49:58.110
The glove only has life when I put my

00:49:58.120 --> 00:50:01.190
hand in it.

00:50:01.200 --> 00:50:04.270
You don't control the gift. I do. Don't

00:50:04.280 --> 00:50:08.110
ever forget

00:50:08.110 --> 00:50:08.120
that."And

00:50:08.120 --> 00:50:10.150
so many of you think,

00:50:10.160 --> 00:50:11.230
"Well, I'm going to go and do this. I'm

00:50:11.240 --> 00:50:14.550
going to do that."Not without me.

00:50:17.640 --> 00:50:22.830
As I sit and I look at my flowers,

00:50:22.840 --> 00:50:23.910
I realize...

00:50:23.920 --> 00:50:25.990
I sit out and I just look at them and let the sun

00:50:26.000 --> 00:50:27.670
just hit my face. I sit there and

00:50:27.680 --> 00:50:30.670
I realize in that stillness,

00:50:30.680 --> 00:50:32.190
Brandon probably doesn't have the

00:50:32.200 --> 00:50:34.750
character to handle that yet.

00:50:34.760 --> 00:50:38.550
I'm not dead enough.

00:50:38.560 --> 00:50:41.390
But he allowed me to do this.

00:50:41.400 --> 00:50:43.430
And I don't ever want anything to

00:50:43.440 --> 00:50:46.750
jeopardize my relationship with him.

00:50:46.760 --> 00:50:49.230
This is just a byproduct of

00:50:49.240 --> 00:50:50.510
something that I've spent years

00:50:50.520 --> 00:50:54.630
cultivating.

00:50:54.640 --> 00:50:56.910
I've listened and

00:50:56.920 --> 00:50:59.870
I listen and I stay at his feet. But if

00:50:59.880 --> 00:51:02.710
money, if fame, if all this can destroy

00:51:02.720 --> 00:51:04.830
me and take me to nothing and cost me my

00:51:04.840 --> 00:51:05.910
marriage,

00:51:05.920 --> 00:51:08.310
who cares? If you can gain the whole

00:51:08.320 --> 00:51:11.670
world and lose your soul...

00:51:11.680 --> 00:51:13.670
they may have the character to

00:51:13.680 --> 00:51:16.110
handle it because God gave it to them, but

00:51:16.110 --> 00:51:16.120
it

00:51:16.120 --> 00:51:18.790
doesn't mean you are.

00:51:18.790 --> 00:51:18.800
It

00:51:18.800 --> 00:51:23.470
doesn't mean you're ready.

00:51:23.480 --> 00:51:24.950
Maybe there's something in you the

00:51:24.960 --> 00:51:28.190
Lord sees, and he says,

00:51:28.200 --> 00:51:30.430
"You're not ready for that yet,

00:51:30.440 --> 00:51:32.230
but I'll allow you to be used at this

00:51:32.240 --> 00:51:34.950
level because

00:51:34.960 --> 00:51:38.310
I need you right

00:51:38.310 --> 00:51:38.320
now."I

00:51:38.320 --> 00:51:40.030
remember sitting out in a Homeland

00:51:40.040 --> 00:51:43.510
parking lot in Guthrie,

00:51:43.510 --> 00:51:43.520
Oklahoma—and

00:51:43.520 --> 00:51:46.790
it was before it was a

00:51:46.790 --> 00:51:46.800
Savers—and

00:51:46.800 --> 00:51:48.950
the Lord told me, he said, "I want

00:51:48.960 --> 00:51:50.550
to use you for the ministry, and

00:51:51.760 --> 00:51:52.830
you're going to bring

00:51:52.840 --> 00:51:54.550
healing to the nations like Oral Roberts,

00:51:54.560 --> 00:51:55.510
and all these things are going to happen

00:51:55.520 --> 00:51:57.870
with you."And I remember sitting there

00:51:57.880 --> 00:51:59.550
and I said, "Lord, if you're going to do

00:51:59.560 --> 00:52:01.830
it, then just do it. I'm tired of

00:52:01.840 --> 00:52:03.270
waiting and hearing you tell me about

00:52:03.280 --> 00:52:04.670
that."And

00:52:04.680 --> 00:52:06.390
boy, I tell you what, that was a

00:52:06.400 --> 00:52:07.990
really stupid

00:52:08.000 --> 00:52:15.190
thing to say.

00:52:15.200 --> 00:52:17.670
We get impatient and we want everything

00:52:17.680 --> 00:52:20.310
to be microwaved. But to go from glory

00:52:20.320 --> 00:52:24.590
to glory takes character.

00:52:24.600 --> 00:52:26.270
And it takes you being stripped away

00:52:26.280 --> 00:52:28.550
from your pride because he doesn't want

00:52:28.560 --> 00:52:30.350
to lose

00:52:30.350 --> 00:52:30.360
you—to

00:52:30.360 --> 00:52:32.390
gain the whole world and lose your

00:52:32.400 --> 00:52:33.550
soul.

00:52:33.560 --> 00:52:36.510
So if God wants you just to pray on

00:52:36.520 --> 00:52:39.150
a YouTube channel of

00:52:39.150 --> 00:52:39.160
mine,

00:52:39.160 --> 00:52:42.350
thank you for being here.

00:52:42.360 --> 00:52:44.270
Thank you. For many hands make

00:52:44.280 --> 00:52:45.670
light work.

00:52:45.680 --> 00:52:47.270
And I believe the best is yet to come

00:52:47.280 --> 00:52:49.470
for every single one of us.

00:52:49.480 --> 00:52:51.830
And we have a part just like this

00:52:51.840 --> 00:52:54.430
guy praying for

00:52:54.430 --> 00:52:54.440
Finney—praying

00:52:54.440 --> 00:52:55.950
for the people down in

00:52:55.950 --> 00:52:55.960
Miami,

00:52:55.960 --> 00:52:57.470
praying for those that go and say,

00:52:57.480 --> 00:52:59.630
"We had 40,000 people,

00:52:59.640 --> 00:53:02.070
we had this, we had

00:53:02.070 --> 00:53:02.080
that."Praise

00:53:02.080 --> 00:53:03.950
God, man.

00:53:03.960 --> 00:53:05.750
Obviously,

00:53:05.760 --> 00:53:08.590
if God thought I could handle it, he

00:53:08.600 --> 00:53:11.190
would give it to me.

00:53:11.200 --> 00:53:14.030
But until then, "Obey me for what I've

00:53:14.040 --> 00:53:17.910
asked you to

00:53:17.910 --> 00:53:17.920
do."And

00:53:17.920 --> 00:53:20.070
sometimes you can have everything

00:53:20.080 --> 00:53:21.950
offered to you and everything under the

00:53:21.960 --> 00:53:24.070
sun being presented to you and the Lord

00:53:24.080 --> 00:53:30.910
says, "Don't touch

00:53:30.910 --> 00:53:30.920
it."Maybe

00:53:30.920 --> 00:53:33.550
he will tomorrow. I don't know.

00:53:33.560 --> 00:53:36.230
All I know is right now. He said no.

00:53:36.240 --> 00:53:38.670
And I get so disappointed. I walk

00:53:38.680 --> 00:53:40.750
away angry about it sometimes. I go, "Why

00:53:40.750 --> 00:53:40.760
me?"kicking

00:53:40.760 --> 00:53:42.230
a rock like a little

00:53:42.240 --> 00:53:44.630
kid.

00:53:44.640 --> 00:53:46.270
I get in the car. I drive around for a

00:53:46.280 --> 00:53:49.190
little bit and pray.

00:53:49.190 --> 00:53:49.200
Diana

00:53:49.200 --> 00:53:51.870
goes...

00:53:51.880 --> 00:53:54.030
I told her today, I said, "Thank God

00:53:54.040 --> 00:53:56.070
you've put up with me

00:53:56.080 --> 00:53:57.750
all these years. You've stood by

00:53:57.760 --> 00:53:59.030
my side even when I act like a

00:53:59.040 --> 00:54:03.030
little brat,

00:54:03.040 --> 00:54:09.190
cranky about something stupid.

00:54:09.200 --> 00:54:13.310
I want to do this. I want to do

00:54:13.310 --> 00:54:13.320
that."But

00:54:13.320 --> 00:54:15.230
I don't want to ever lose the

00:54:15.240 --> 00:54:17.990
ability to hear him like I do.

00:54:18.000 --> 00:54:21.790
When he comes and visits...

00:54:21.800 --> 00:54:23.190
he'll come and visit and he'll sit down

00:54:23.200 --> 00:54:25.030
and we'll talk,

00:54:25.040 --> 00:54:27.630
and the Holy Spirit is so real

00:54:27.640 --> 00:54:29.390
and the presence of the Lord

00:54:29.400 --> 00:54:31.430
fills my whole house.

00:54:31.440 --> 00:54:32.670
And I'll be able to see over into the

00:54:32.680 --> 00:54:34.830
other side—angels

00:54:34.830 --> 00:54:34.840
in

00:54:34.840 --> 00:54:38.390
heaven and beautiful things.

00:54:38.400 --> 00:54:40.150
But if you were to gain the whole world

00:54:40.160 --> 00:54:46.830
and lose that, who cares?

00:54:46.840 --> 00:54:48.270
There's something that I...

00:54:48.280 --> 00:54:50.790
this is worth more to me:

00:54:50.800 --> 00:54:52.470
to have a relationship with him and

00:54:52.480 --> 00:54:54.030
know what's coming and warn the

00:54:54.040 --> 00:54:56.030
people as much as I can. The ones that

00:54:56.040 --> 00:55:00.830
will listen.

00:55:00.840 --> 00:55:03.710
And live by myself—be by myself, you

00:55:03.720 --> 00:55:05.190
know, with hardly any friends or

00:55:05.190 --> 00:55:05.200
whatever—and

00:55:05.200 --> 00:55:07.470
just be following the Holy

00:55:07.480 --> 00:55:10.150
Ghost

00:55:10.160 --> 00:55:11.950
and just say, "Hey, at least I know that

00:55:11.960 --> 00:55:14.990
all my family—my mom, my dad, my

00:55:15.000 --> 00:55:16.990
brothers, my sisters—are all serving the

00:55:17.000 --> 00:55:19.510
Lord. We all love the Lord. We all are

00:55:19.520 --> 00:55:21.270
baptized in the Holy Ghost. We pray in

00:55:21.280 --> 00:55:23.670
tongues, casting out

00:55:23.670 --> 00:55:23.680
devils."You

00:55:23.680 --> 00:55:25.750
have to believe, hey, that stands

00:55:25.760 --> 00:55:27.630
for a lot.

00:55:27.640 --> 00:55:29.350
Regardless if your name is known

00:55:29.360 --> 00:55:31.150
throughout the whole world and you're

00:55:31.160 --> 00:55:33.270
having a huge auditorium full of people

00:55:33.280 --> 00:55:35.030
and everybody's clapping and saying

00:55:35.040 --> 00:55:37.150
whatever.

00:55:37.160 --> 00:55:38.950
People's opinions change. I've seen it on

00:55:38.960 --> 00:55:42.350
this internet and it is toxic.

00:55:42.360 --> 00:55:43.350
Does that make sense what I'm trying to

00:55:43.360 --> 00:55:44.510
tell y'all?

00:55:44.520 --> 00:55:47.430
I try to present my life

00:55:47.430 --> 00:55:47.440
and

00:55:47.440 --> 00:55:49.150
what I'm learning

00:55:49.160 --> 00:55:51.590
just by things that I see,

00:55:51.590 --> 00:55:51.600
because

00:55:51.600 --> 00:55:54.830
I see so much.

00:55:54.840 --> 00:55:57.470
And I want you to really search your

00:55:57.480 --> 00:56:00.750
heart tonight and really know him.

00:56:00.760 --> 00:56:03.790
And it's not in all the hype.

00:56:03.800 --> 00:56:07.390
He's in that still small voice.

00:56:07.400 --> 00:56:09.350
He's not in the lights. He's not in the

00:56:09.360 --> 00:56:12.430
spotlight. He's not in all the junk.

00:56:12.440 --> 00:56:14.830
He's in that still small voice inside of

00:56:14.840 --> 00:56:17.630
you. And when you get real—oh

00:56:17.630 --> 00:56:17.640
God—and

00:56:17.640 --> 00:56:20.150
you crucify yourself, crucify

00:56:20.160 --> 00:56:21.790
your flesh daily.

00:56:21.800 --> 00:56:23.790
I die daily.

00:56:23.800 --> 00:56:26.710
I die daily. What is it that keeps you

00:56:26.720 --> 00:56:29.550
dead? Don't resurrect the old man. What

00:56:29.560 --> 00:56:31.790
keeps you dead?

00:56:31.800 --> 00:56:33.830
So that you are crucified with Christ;

00:56:33.840 --> 00:56:35.590
nevertheless, Christ in me, the hope of

00:56:35.600 --> 00:56:38.990
glory. I am so sold out to him that in

00:56:39.000 --> 00:56:41.270
these last days when he says, "Go and do

00:56:41.280 --> 00:56:43.550
this, do that,"I want to be obedient.

00:56:43.560 --> 00:56:47.630
Quickly obey. Quickly obey.

00:56:47.640 --> 00:56:51.870
Whatever he says for you to do, do it.

00:56:51.880 --> 00:56:53.190
So if you're here tonight and you say,

00:56:53.190 --> 00:56:53.200
"Brandon,

00:56:53.200 --> 00:56:55.190
I just wish you could pray

00:56:55.200 --> 00:56:57.630
for me.

00:56:57.640 --> 00:56:58.870
Could you pray for me? I'm not right

00:56:58.880 --> 00:57:01.110
with the Lord.

00:57:01.120 --> 00:57:03.510
You say all of these things and I feel

00:57:03.520 --> 00:57:05.270
inside of myself, man, I have so far to

00:57:05.280 --> 00:57:06.390
go."We

00:57:06.400 --> 00:57:08.550
all do. We're all a work in progress.

00:57:08.560 --> 00:57:11.190
None of us have perfected any of this.

00:57:11.200 --> 00:57:12.390
